 countless, whatever your mood or activities. With so many incredible aromas to select from, there is always going to be a scent which can lift your spirits and improve your productivity for the day. Whether you plan to spend your day working energetically or taking a well-earned break, essential oils make the perfect accompaniment.<br><br>Unlike air fresheners and candles, essential oils work to cleanse and purify the air, filling it with a fresh and crisp scent without any harmful or harsh chemicals to inhale. For example, <a href="/products/eucalyptus-essential-oil" target="_self">eucalyptus</a> and <a href="/products/tea-tree-essential-oil" target="_self">tea tree essential oils</a> are renowned for their abilities to remove yeast and mould particles from the air. They work to remove harmful bacteria by breaking down free radicals lingering in the air and creating an environment that is inhospitable to them.
